Job Description:Food Service Area Supervisor Location: Massachusetts Salary: Competitive The Company: The reputable international Sushi brand ensures quality, consistency, and great value is at the core of every sushi roll they produce. It is their number one priority to provide their customers with hand-crafted, quality food using only the freshest ingredients available. Conveniently located in 'grab and go' kiosks and sushi bars in supermarkets, shopping centres, corporate dining facilities and schools across Canada and the United States, our client is committed to delivering quick, fresh and convenient products you can feel good about eating. The Role: What We Look For:1 year of experience in a supervisory capacity within food services; preferably in a multi-unit environmentAbility to adapt and succeed in a fast paced environmentMust be self-motivated and customer focused orientedAbility to prioritize tasks and work well under pressure and deal with stressful situationsAbility to travel within an assigned region with a flexible schedule to accommodate operational needs. What We Offer:Competitive SalaryBenefits including health, dental, life insurance and long term disabilityBonus/Incentive planCar Allowance and gas cardCareer advancement opportunities Food Service Supervisor Responsibilities:Responsible for driving operational excellence within an assigned area including managing financial performance and maintaining high levels of satisfaction with services to guests and customersHire, train and lead a team ensuring operating standards are adhered to including: food quality and safety, guest experience, productivity, and health and safetyDrive the rollout and implementation of new programs and initiatives i.e. implementation of new store openings, new product roll outs and marketing programsRoutinely visit assigned stored, ensuring the Company's policies and procedures are properly executedBuild and maintain strong customer relationships with store management and third party auditors COREcruitment are experts in recruiting for the service sector. We currently have over 700 live roles across the UK, Middle East, Europe, North America, South East Asia, Africa and Australia. To view other great opportunities please check out our website at Follow COREcruitment on your favourite social networks Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn andPinterest . We give away fantastic prizes... every month!
